***Activity time tracker

-For tracking the amount of time spent on an activity – for this example, practicing art
     *But could track studying, coding, practicing a language, playing video games, sports, training, workouts....
-Saves the date the activity was done on
-The number of hours
-The type – in this example, drawing, painting and sketching
    *An example of using a select-option input
-The medium – in this example, digital or traditional (on paper/canvas)
    *Example of using radio buttons

